    Page: 356
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Peace/Harmony
---
If you really want peace of mind and inner calm, you will get it.
Regardless of how unjustly you have been treated, or how unfair the boss
has been, or what a mean scoundrel someone has proved to be, all this makes
no difference to you when you awaken to your mental and spiritual powers.
